  <brief_title>According CTC to Compare the Influences of Different Methods to Remove the PDAC</brief_title>
  <official_title>To Compare the Influences of Different Methods to Remove the Pancreatic Ductal Adenocarcinoma With the Detection of Circulating Tumor Cells</official_title>
