  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Acccording circulating tumor cells to compare the differences of different methods(routine
      method、no-touch principle method、laparoscopy method) to remove the ductal adenocarcinoma of
      pancreatic body and tail.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
